title: "Rust and NSString part 2"
date: 2021-11-06T13:47:39+01:00
image: https://res.cloudinary.com/barhamon/image/upload/v1626989237/rust_and_nsstring/header.png
preview: "How NSString::UTF8String actually works"
tags:
- rust
