title: "The southern part of TET Turkey ride"
date: 2023-05-14T15:23:47+02:00
image: https://res.cloudinary.com/barhamon/image/upload/c_scale,h_800,q_auto/v1698169652/tet-turkey/ride/route/1_-_19_rl7bqj.jpg
